title: [Dabbings Mews, Talbot Court]
description: Tall, thin houses ring the court, their facades immaculate.  A few halfling children chase each other down the narrow alleys created by the residences' closely set foundations.  Pushed by the demanding Icemulian wind, clouds fly swiftly overhead, casting enormous shadows that dwarf the buildings below.

Tall, thin houses ring the court, their facades immaculate.  Only a few muffled footsteps suggest the presence of halflings as they walk swiftly down the narrow alleys created by the residences' closely set foundations.  Pushed by the demanding Icemulian wind, clouds fly swiftly overhead, casting the buildings below into total darkness.
